extendedInfo.description: Top 200 Rx Prescription Brand Name Drugs Brand and their Generics equivalents in a great little Multiple Choice Quiz, Flash cards and a handy Android sized Dictionary for learning on the go. Perfect for Pharmacists who need to keep their edge.

reviews.title: Iffy
reviews.comment: Save yourself the trouble and make your own cards.  Some of them are incorrect and the multiple choice quiz sometimes has the wrong answers and sometimes has the right answer twice, one of which is wrong.
reviews.author: Chase Louviere

reviews.comment: Thought this would be helpful to practice my brand and generics...but some of the names of the drugs are completely wrong/incorrect matches!!!
reviews.author: A Google User
